What data structure is pictured in <image 1>?

A. Singly linked list
B. Doubly linked list
C. Circularly linked list
D. Array
E. None of the other answers

The image depicts a sequence of nodes where each node contains some data and a pointer to the next node. The last node points to `null`, indicating the end of the list. This structure is characteristic of a singly linked list, where each node has a single pointer to the next node in the sequence.

Therefore, the correct answer is:

A. Singly linked list
